```json
{
"application": "CaMa-Flood",
"details": {
"software": "CaMa-Flood",
"version": "v3.96a",
"language": "Fortran",
"input": {
"forcing": {
"type": "plain binary",
"format": ".one",
"frequency": "daily",
"unit": "mm/day",
"conversion_factor": "86400000 (mm/day->m/s)",
"directory": "CaMa_in/$runname/Roff_TRUE",
"prefix": "Roff__",
"suffix": "T000.one",
"interpolation": "interpolated with input matrix",
"input matrix": "inpmat_test-1deg.bin"
},
"map": {
"type": "plain binary",
"format": ".bin",
"directory": "map",
"files": {
"nextxy": "nextxy.bin",
"ctmare": "ctmare.bin",
"elevtn": "elevtn.bin",
"nxtdst": "nxtdst.bin",
"rivlen": "rivlen.bin",
"fldhgt": "fldhgt.bin",
"rivwth": "rivwth_gwdlr.bin",
"rivhgt": "rivhgt_Xudong.bin",
"rivman": "rivmanTRUE.bin"
},
"dimension info": "diminfo_test-1deg.txt"
},
"restart": {
"type": "binary",
"format": ".bin",
"frequency": "end of run",
"directory": ".",
"prefix": "restart",
"suffix": ".bin"
}
},
"output": {
"type": "binary",
"format": ".bin",
"frequency": "daily",
"directory": "CaMa_out/$EXP",
"variables": [
"rivout",
"rivsto",
"sfcelv",
"outflw",
"storge",
"fldout",
"fldsto"
]
},
"resources": {
"cpu": "20",
"memory": "10gb"
}
}
}
```
